Job responsibilities:
Perform due diligence in the existing IT/cloud architecture of the customers, understand the technical landscape of the Internet companies or large and medium-sized enterprises, and support the onboarding, implementation and delivery of the design of IT/cloud solutions;
Develop service solutions that meet customer requirements through HUAWEI CLOUD technical architecture;Support the migration of customers existing application systems and data to HUAWEI CLOUD by designing and implementing the migration solutions, managing and providing the technical support for the entire migration process;
Work on the cloud POC, guide and solve the issues during the POC;
Regularly communicate with customers (on-site or remotely) on the technical issues;
Ensure the healthy and stable running of cloud services and improve customer experience.
Job requirements
Experienced in cloud computing design, migration, and delivery service. Be familiar with virtualization architectures such as OpenStack and mainstream public cloud services;
Experienced in operation and maintenance of IT infrastructure (including server, storage, database, network, middleware, mainstream file system); Experience in enterprise-level application architecture design or cloud service integration implementation is preferred;
Familiar with mainstream database or middleware, maintenance, migration or backup for one of the mainstream databases (such as Oracle, MySQL or SQL server). Familiar with common operating systems (Linux/Windows), network-related knowledge (DNS/BGP/VPN/ELB/IP), software development, post-sales service, or O&M experience is preferred;
Knowledge in the test process, and documentation capabilities
Good communications, coordination and resource integration skills;
Curiosity with a strong learning drive.
Interested candidate who wish to apply for this position, please click on APPLY NOW
